description: Try our easy to follow Turkey Tacos  recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Turkey Tacos Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 can black beans no added salt, drained

recipeInstructions.text: In a large skillet at medium heart add onions, garlic, cumin, paprika and Turkey mince.
Season with salt and pepper and stir using a wooden spoon to break the lumps. Cook for 10 minutes or until the turkey mince its brown and cooked
Portion out the beans, corn, coriander, & spring onions in small bowls
On a flat surface place, the taco and top with 2 tablespoons turkey, add beans, corn, coriander and spring opinions and top it with Cheese. Optional to add some guacamole
